Hello, it's great to hear that you're thinking carefully about your relationship with food.

Here are a few things to consider. Here are some things to consider for healthy eating habits:&#x20;

Eat Regularly: Eat three main meals a day, with snacks in between if you need them. Make an effort to eat a variety of nutrient-dense foods, including fruits, vegetables, whole grains, lean proteins, and healthy fats. These foods will help you feel full and satisfied, and will also give your body the nutrients it needs to function properly.
